com.solvvy.extractor.stepwise

Class BasicStepParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.solvvy.extractor.stepwise.BasicStepParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StepParser

    public class BasicStepParser
extends Object
implements StepParser
    A basic stepwise-solution parser that treats top-level list-item elements as individual steps. Does not account for recursive lists.
